race.description: Hanging Rock New Years Day Races Bm62 Handicap
race.comment: DEMARCATE (12) hasn't really fired in two runs back from a spell but will be fitter for them and this is easier than what he's been facing. Giving him one more from the ideal gate in what looks a winnable race. VIASAIN (11) resumes. His form was mixed last time in but the best of it reads well. Like this trip for him and he's got the pace to roll forward and will take catching from there. MARTY MCFLY (9) has won two on the bounce and has to be respected despite going up in grade again. STAR DIESEL (2) resumes. His form last time in was good, not far away in a BM58 at Seymour fresh last campaign before winning over this route. He's up to winning this.
